@@ -0,0 +1,12 @@
+# FocusedEditableTextWatcher Object
+
+* `close` Function - Stops the watcher. Calling this more than once has no
+  effect.
+
+The watcher is returned by
+[`webContents.watchFocusedEditableText`](../web-contents.md#contentswatchfocusededitabletextoptions-callback).
+It owns one focused editable text subscription for one `WebContents`.
+
+The watcher remains active even if JavaScript does not retain the returned
+object. Keep the returned object when the watcher should be closed before the
+WebContents is destroyed.
